    "body": "Before standard json only that \"combined json\" (for output) option existed on the CLI, but the emscripten version had other JSON methods (`compileSingle`, `compileMulti`, `compileJSON`).\r\n\r\n`solc-js` has a backward compatible wrapper, so that it will use the old interfaces, but the earlier you go the less it can do (such as very early versions didn't support multiple files).  If you need to use the CLI, then this is of no help.",
